Package com.oose2015.group13.backend

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AI
    AI class, a subclass of Player.
    Board
    Game Board object.
    Game
    Game describes the current game like the game state, who all are playing, whose turn it is etc.
    GameController
    GameController controls the Game Service and handles Game related requests
    GameService
    GameService acts as an interface between the GameController and all the functions related to the game
    Piece
    Piece describes a game piece such as Carrier, Destroyer, Aircraft Carrier, etc.
    Player
    Player class saves the details of the players of a game.
    Settings
    Settings object, which each User has.
    Tile
    Tile represents an X and Y coordinate on the game board.
    User
    User class temporarily saves information about the current user
    UserController
    UserController controls the UserService and handles User related requests
    UserService
    UserService acts as an interface between UserController and functions for user
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    LoginType
    LoginType returns the type of login that the user has chosen
    PieceType
    PieceType describes a Piece.
    Result
    Result enum describes the result of a move or attack.
    Status
    Status enum describes status of the Game (whether we are waiting for players, or the game is over, etc...)
    TileType
    TileType describes a Tile object.
